<p style="position: relative">The Hoops have rarely found goalscoring form hard to come by in recent seasons, but a number of strikers have arrived, yet failed to flourish in the green and white.</p>
<p style="position: relative">It has to be said since 2020, we&#8217;ve had a fair few strikers come and go, with many of them making little or no impact.</p>
<p style="position: relative">We&#8217;re going back through the years before that too, so those of you of an older generation will have to jog your memories on some of them.</p>
<p style="position: relative">I&#8217;ve given you 24 multiple choice questions to answer, see how many you can get right.</p>
<p style="position: relative">It has to be said, there&#8217;s a few duds in there!</p>
<p style="position: relative">So, just how well can you remember some of Celtic&#8217;s obscure, previous forwards?</p>
