<p style="position: relative">I&#8217;ve often discussed the money we&#8217;ve spent on players that didn&#8217;t work out.</p>
<p style="position: relative">If you read my articles on that subject, the amounts of money we&#8217;ve wasted on duds might actually shock you.</p>
<p style="position: relative">But for every ten duds we buy, there&#8217;s always one gem, and In suppose that&#8217;s the way the board looks at it.</p>
<p style="position: relative">Some of the arrivals in this quiz didn&#8217;t exactly make the impact they would&#8217;ve hoped in Glasgow, with their departures going under the radar.</p>
<p style="position: relative">There&#8217;s one in particular that still has me scratching my head!</p>
<p style="position: relative">Today&#8217;s picture quiz is all about some of them, where we&#8217;ve tasked you to pick out 20 forgotten Hoops departures over the last 20 plus years.</p>
<p style="position: relative">We&#8217;ve given you three possible options and the season they left the club.</p>
